%% Diagram: thresholdIndex transitions for threshold = [0, 0.5, 1.0]
%% Type: stateDiagram
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR
  [*] --> Outside: first observation<br/>previousThresholdIndex = -1<br/>previousIsIntersecting = false
  Outside --> Partial: any pixel intersects<br/>thresholdIndex = 1<br/>isIntersecting = true
  Partial --> HalfPlus: ratio crosses 0.5<br/>thresholdIndex = 2
  HalfPlus --> FullCover: ratio reaches 1.0<br/>thresholdIndex = 3
  FullCover --> HalfPlus: ratio drops below 1.0<br/>thresholdIndex = 2
  HalfPlus --> Partial: ratio drops below 0.5<br/>thresholdIndex = 1
  Partial --> Outside: target leaves root<br/>isIntersecting = false<br/>(thresholdIndex stays 1)

  note right of Outside
    Default threshold = [0]
    collapses to two effective
    states: Outside and Inside,
    differentiated only by
    isIntersecting.
  end note
